name: Generative-Lights: Acid
description: HD 2K mp4 (1280x1280) for square displays, by Tono C @toocabanelas. Generative-Lights is a series of analog experiments that mix captured light in real time with the interaction of sound. This piece is shot with an ultra HD (6k) cinema camera, a super bright telephoto lens (0.95 f) and a high frame rate per second (160 fps). The image, colors and shapes are 100% analog and not digital.
